data.description: This 1,155 square foot 2-3 bedroom/1.5 bath ranch home with a 2 car attached garage in the Old Mill Grove Subdivision is available for immediate occupancy. Oak floors throughout most of the home add a special ambiance and quality to this home. Kitchen with adjacent dining room offers plenty of space. Kitchen features 42" upper cabinets and a pantry closet for plenty of storage. Wall between the 2nd and 3rd bedrooms has been removed and will need to be re-installed to have 3 bedrooms again. Utility room off the kitchen and garage is ideal space to shed those coats and shoes/boots etc so you don't track up the home. There is also a door to the back yard from the utility room so if you are working in the fenced back yard you can shed your work clothes/outfit in the utility room too! 2 car garage features 2 good sized storage rooms for your tools/equipment or the toys/bikes etc. Come and make this your next home!!! This is a Fannie Mae Homepath property.
